summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department authorizing the sale and conveyance by Quitclaim Deed of a portion of real property commonly known as the Lake Youngs Aqueduct Right-of-Way (LYA R/W) located in Section 17, Township 22 North, Range 6 East, W.M., King County, Washington to COLIN MCDONALD AND DORA MCDONALD, husband and wife.
